Class ProjectRegistry

Object
ProjectRegistry
public class ProjectRegistry extends Object
Registry for storing and retrieving BTO projects by name. Provides static methods to manage the project collection in memory, including loading, filtering, retrieval, and validation utilities. This registry is used globally by managers, officers, and applicants to access projects.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Javier
